      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This dependable ride is the perfect choice for anyone seeking a solid, functional vehicle at a great value! While it shows some honest signs of its journey and has a bit of character from regular use, it remains a reliable performer that gets the job done. It's a practical, budget-friendly option that's ready to hit the road with its next owner today!",
