    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major restoration project or a donor for parts. The engine is not currently running and will require a comprehensive rebuild, while the body shows significant signs of age, including noticeable rust and peeling clear coat. The interior has sustained heavy wear and tear, and the electrical system needs troubleshooting. It is sold as-is, reflecting its need for substantial repair to return to the road.",
