    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming adventures! I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This 3.2L straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to provide exceptional throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed: the rear subframe is reinforced, and both rod bearings and the VANOS hub have been addressed. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings, though the exterior reflects honest age. This is a mechanically sorted driver's car ready for the apex.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
