    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather seating is plush and intact, showing only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and the premium surround-sound system, is in full working order. Mechanically, this car is sound\u2014it shifts smoothly through all gears and the engine idle is whisper-quiet. It has been serviced regularly with synthetic oil, and the brake pads were recently replaced. This car represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-spec vehicle that has been treated with respect. Full service logs are available for review.",
      "price": 34500.0,
